<section class="rules" id="rules" aria-labelledby="rules-h">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-label"><span class="n">02</span><h2 id="rules-h">Safer space</h2></div>
    <p class="rules__intro">By entering, you agree to Module's shared guidelines — everyone here is entitled to a space free from harassment, discrimination and exclusion. All genders, skin tones, sexual orientations, ages and body types are welcome. Consent, turned all the way up.</p>
    <div class="rules__grid">
      <div class="rule rule--wide">
        <div class="rule__n">01 — THE GROUND RULE</div>
        <div class="rule__t">Only an enthusiastic, verbal YES is a yes.</div>
        <div class="rule__d">No means no. Silence means no. Mumbling means no. Uncomfortable body language means no. Anything that isn't a clear yes is a no.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule">
        <div class="rule__n">02</div>
        <div class="rule__t">No physical contact without clear consent.</div>
        <div class="rule__d">Ask, every time, everyone. There are no exceptions, no matter how far the night has come.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule">
        <div class="rule__n">03</div>
        <div class="rule__t">Zero tolerance.</div>
        <div class="rule__d">Racism, sexism, homophobia and transphobia will not be tolerated. Cross the line and you're out — and you stay out.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule">
        <div class="rule__n">04</div>
        <div class="rule__t">No staring or intrusive behaviour.</div>
        <div class="rule__d">Looking is fine — respect boundaries. Give people the room to be here on their own terms.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule">
        <div class="rule__n">05</div>
        <div class="rule__t">No photos or video inside the club.</div>
        <div class="rule__d">Phones away; your camera is covered at the door. It protects everyone — including you. What happens on the floor stays on the floor.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule">
        <div class="rule__n">06</div>
        <div class="rule__t">Our staff and awareness team are here for you.</div>
        <div class="rule__d">Feel uncomfortable, or see a boundary crossed? Reach out immediately — they're easy to find. We'll believe you, and we'll help.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

